Package: SlideCNA
Title: Calls Copy Number Alterations from Slide-seq data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Diane",
           family = "Zhang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dkzhang711@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0268-4413"))
Description: This takes spatial single-cell-type RNA-seq data (specifically designed for Slide-seq v2) that calls copy number alterations (CNAs) using pseudospatial binning, clusters cellular units (e.g. beads) based on CNA profile, and visualizes spatial CNA patterns.
